{"tid":689531,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"放鬆啲啦香港人！","createTime":"2018-06-04T07:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T07:29:15.000Z","uid":181112,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9183b99b0ab9987e32b4993dbb559dab543ef4a7","tid":689531,"uid":181112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:00:46.000Z","msg":"事緣琴日同班朋友揸車去沙灘, 去到個公共停車場位已經好爆, 我哋就兵分兩路, 我同一個女仔落沙灘預備好先, 另一邊就等車位.<br />\n<br />\n咁啱我地落緊沙灘嘅時間見到有個車位, 又冇車, 我就即刻打俾個friend叫佢揸過嚟, 過咗20秒左右有一格中港牌嘅私家車停咗係我哋前面話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 中港牌男<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你行開啲, 我要泊呢個位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好意思啊, 格車過緊嚟㗎啦, 好快就到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咁樣唔啱規矩喎, 用個人霸主個位得嫁咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好意思啊 (之後我再call個friend )<br />\n<br />\n當我再打俾我朋友嘅時候, 個中港男已經將架車插左半個車位入去, 之後已經攞起個電話用鏡頭對住我話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你都唔想我拍片等網絡公審你嫁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 格車到啦依家係你後面<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咁樣唔啱規矩 (一路拍緊)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到最後個車位都係俾咗佢, 雖然我唔知道用人黎霸住個車位啱唔啱規矩, 但我同呢位中港男對話唔夠30秒, 佢已經拎起個電話想網絡公審我, 只能講一句放鬆啲啦香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3e167b5f09dc9bc0a88b7145564e18e23cc443","tid":689531,"uid":62020,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:03:40.000Z","msg":"咁真係你唔岩喎<br />\n同啲街霸用凳霸咪錶位有咩分別<br />\n關鍵不在時間上 係你果陣都無車係手"},{"pid":"746d2f2bce93f4cdb05276a04ebb9e134ba17234","tid":689531,"uid":181112,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"cc3e167b5f09dc9bc0a88b7145564e18e23cc443","tid":689531,"uid":62020,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:03:40.000Z","msg":"咁真係你唔岩喎<br />\n同啲街霸用凳霸咪錶位有咩分別<br />\n關鍵不在時間上 係你果陣都無車係手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:05:56.000Z","msg":"其實之後同朋友講返都知係唔啱嘅<br />\n但我覺得心平氣和唔啱咪講到岩, 唔需要下下都話要公審<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e3f9b73a8e129a98f9f0283729dec912791bee","tid":689531,"uid":70439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:08:10.000Z","msg":"樓豬等比人屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618a7f8fe8491eaa00f152b60e021fac25201934","tid":689531,"uid":62020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"746d2f2bce93f4cdb05276a04ebb9e134ba17234","tid":689531,"uid":181112,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"cc3e167b5f09dc9bc0a88b7145564e18e23cc443","tid":689531,"uid":62020,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:03:40.000Z","msg":"咁真係你唔岩喎<br />\n同啲街霸用凳霸咪錶位有咩分別<br />\n關鍵不在時間上 係你果陣都無車係手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:05:56.000Z","msg":"其實之後同朋友講返都知係唔啱嘅<br />\n但我覺得心平氣和唔啱咪講到岩, 唔需要下下都話要公審<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:08:11.000Z","msg":"可能人地真係趕時間呢 你仲企係度塞住人<br />\n人地唔嬲都有鬼啦 你咪又係上連登諗住屌人同搏同情<br />\n<br />\n有無將心比己過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上高登打一大段字加幾個表情就想人同情你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"dd5585c76368c1010622abd504a6224a3f102112",